<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_108" id="53r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_108_r1l4">VVılhelm Mendel vnd <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Ortlyeb </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_108_r1l5"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> wir hetten den göldlein geſant ʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ den fürſten vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l6">von den wır denn <expan>gewönlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das geleyt ʒu vnd von der meſſ beſtellen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l7">ſıe ſunderlıch ʒu erynnern von vnſers <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> ſtepfans handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l8">etc / Der hat das alſo geworben / vnd ıſt ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ſagt vns wıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l9"><expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vnd ır amptleẅt vaſt melden daʒ etlıch dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vaſt on </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l10">geleyt hin vnd her ʒıehen vnd <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / Daran ſıe vns kein <expan>gefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tun / Doch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l11"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſıe Jm <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> ſıe <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ʒu dıſem mal <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ıren fleıſſ tun dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l12"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Jr leıb vnd ir gut / dıe denn geleyt nemen vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ſıcher ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l13">geleyten / Welh dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> aber nıht geleyt neͣmen vnd bey Jn <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>vvıd<ex>er</ex>für</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l14">den ıcht / darumb <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſıe nıht ʒu kentnuſſ ſteen / Das <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künden</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l15">eẅch / Daʒ Jr das <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auch <expan>ʒuwıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> tuet vnd von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l16"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ſaget / daʒ ſıe ſıch mıt Jren <expan>leıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> fürſehen geleyt <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l17">vnd on geleyt nıht <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch faren / Daran tut Jr vnd ſıe <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l18"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex></expan> ſıgıllo . ſebaldȷ pfıncʒıng <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıciuiu<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_108_r1l19"><expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> Judıca </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_108" id="53r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wilhelm Mendel und <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Ortlyeb </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir hetten den Göldlein gesant zu
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, den fürsten und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von den wir denn
                                <expan>gewönlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das geleyt zu und von der mess
                        bestellen, sie sunderlich zu erynnern von unsers
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Stepfans handels
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. Der hat das also geworben und ist zu
                        uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und sagt uns, wie
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> und ir amptlewt vast melden, daz etlich die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vast on geleyt hin und her ziehen und
                                <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daran sie uns kein
                                <expan>gefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tun; doch
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie im <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>,
                        sie <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zu disem mal <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        iren fleiss tun, die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ir leib und ir gut, die
                        denn geleyt nemen und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, sicher zu geleyten.
                        Welh die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> aber niht geleyt neͣmen und bey in
                                <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex>für</expan>, den icht darumb
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie niht zu kentnuss steen; das
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>künden</expan> wir ewch, daz ir das
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        auch <expan>zu wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> tuet und von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> saget, daz sie sich mit iren
                                <expan>leibe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        fürsehen geleyt <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> und on geleyt niht
                                <expan>wand<ex>er</ex>n</expan> noch faren. Daran tut ir und sie
                                <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo Sebaldi Pfinczing
                                <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> judica.</ab>
</div>
